high_descs: Move to the counter to the left of the sink
Pick up the scoop from the counter
Move to the counter on the right of the sink
Put the scoop on a pan in the cabinet
Pick up the pan from the cabinet
Move to the sink to the left
Put the pan in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a pan in the sink with a scoop on it.

high_descs: Walk forward to the wall then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the ice cream scoop that is touching the coffee maker.
Turn right and walk to the salt shaker on the counter to your left and then turn left to face it.
Open the cupboard above the salt shaker and put the ice cream scoop in the frying pan.
Pick up the frying pan with the ice cream scoop in it.
Turn left and walk to the sink that's on your right then turn right to face it.
Put the frying pan with the ice cream scoop in it in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a frying pan with an ice cream scoop in it in the frying pan.

high_descs: turn right and move towards the coffee maker
pick up the spoon at the right hand side of the coffee maker
turn right and head towards the sink
place the spoon in the pan inside the cupboard above the sink
pick up the pan
turn left towards the sink
drop the pan inside the sink
anns.task_desc: drop a pan with a spoon in it inside the sink
